## 0.1.beta.1

- Update dependencies
- Update image-rs to 0.24.7
    * WebP/TIFF: Adds ICC profile support to TIFF and WebP
    * WebP: Fixes frequent decoding issues
- WebP: Use transparent background instead of color suggested by image in
  animations
